T04TD3973E:254a-1: a'a patti de sha na bi dhi /
T04TD3973E:254a-3: ltung ba bshags pa'i cho ga / thams cad mkhyen pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T04TD3973E:254a-4: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol //
T04TD3973E:254a-5: bdag dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi ba byis pa nyid dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-6: mi shes pa nyid kyis 'dod chags dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-12: tshul khrims ma bsgoms pa dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-13: shes rab ma bsgoms pa dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-14: dran pa nyams pa nyid kyis /
T04TD3973E:254a-15: lus dang ngag dang yid kyis dge slong dang rjes su mthun pa ma lags pa bgyis pa dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-17: gzhan bgyid pa la rjes su yi rang ba de dag thams cad /
T04TD3973E:254a-18: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams la bzod par gsol gyis bzod par mdzad du gsol /
T04TD3973E:254a-19: khyed la ji ltar bzod par gsol ba de bzhin du mkhan po dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-22: chos dang lta ba mthun pa dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-23: rtag tu rjes su 'brang ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-24: gtsug lag khang dang brang khang na gnyug mar gnas pa'i lha dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-25: lam dang nye ba'i lam na gnyug mar gnas pa'i lha dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-26: bstan pa 'di la mngon par dga' ba'i lha dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-27: gzhan gyi bstan pa la mngon par dga' ba'i lha dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-32: ji srid srid pa'i rtse mo'i bar gyi sems can te /
T04TD3973E:254a-33: 'phrog ma'i bu lnga brgya 'khor dang bcas pa dang /
T04TD3973E:254a-34: nag po chen po la sogs pa phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten na gnas pa'i sems can thams cad la nongs pa bgyis pa gang lags pa de bdag gi tshul khrims kyi phung po la sogs pa yongs su rdzogs par bgyi ba'i slad du bzod par gsol gyis bzod par mdzad du gsol /
T04TD3973E:254a-35: de bzhin lan gnyis lan gsum du bzlas /
T04TD3973E:254a-38: dge 'dun btsun pa rnams dgongs su gsol //
T04TD3973E:254a-39: bdag dge slong ming 'di zhes bgyi bas ltung ba rigs lnga po dag la /
T04TD3973E:254b-0: lus dang ngag dang yid kyis sbyor @254b ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-1: dngos gzhi dang mjug rnams su /
T04TD3973E:254b-2: 'dod chags kyis kun nas bslang ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-3: zhe sdang gis kun nas bslang ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-4: gti mug gis kun nas bslang ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-5: chad pas kun nas bslang ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-6: skyed kyis kun nas bslang ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-7: de'i tshan du gtogs pa dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-9: de'i rigs su gtogs pa dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-13: nang du zhag lon pa dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-17: kha bkang nas smra ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-19: byin len ma byas pa dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-21: dus ma yin pa'i zas te /
T04TD3973E:254b-22: mdor na phas pham pa'i chos bzhi dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-23: des kun nas bslang ba'i ltung ba spom po sbyor ba dang dngos gzhi dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-25: dge 'dun lhag ma'i chos bcu gsum dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-26: des kun nas bslang ba'i nyes pa sbom po sbyor ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-29: spang ba'i ltung byed kyi chos sum cu dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-30: des kun nas bslang ba'i nyes pa sbyor ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-33: ltung byed kyi chos bcu dgu dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-34: des kun nas bslang ba'i nyes pa sbyor ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-37: so sor bshags par bya ba'i chos bzhi dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-38: des kun nas bslang ba'i nyes pa sbyor ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-41: bslab par bya ba'i chos brgya rtsa mang po dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-42: des kun nas bslang ba'i nyes pa sbyor ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-45: rtsod pa nye bar zhi bar bya ba'i chos bdun dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-46: des kun nas bslang ba'i nyes pa sbyor ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-50: gzhan yang gang sangs rgyas kyis bcas pa'i bslab pa dang 'gal ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-51: dge 'dun gyis bcas pa'i nang khrims dral ba dang /
T04TD3973E:254b-53: gos par bgyis pa de dag thams cad bdag gi tshul khrims kyi phung po la sogs pa yongs su rdzogs par bgyi ba'i slad du /
T04TD3973E:254b-54: dge 'dun gyi spyan sngar mi 'chab pa'i sems kyis mtho lo bshags so //
T04TD3973E:254b-55: mthol zhing bshags na bdag bde ba la reg par gnas par 'gyur gyi /
T04TD3973E:254b-56: ma mthol ma bshags na de ltar mi 'gyur lags so //
T04TD3973E:255a-1: lan gnyis lan gsum du bzlas /
T04TD3973E:255a-2: ltung ba de dag la ltung bar mthong ngam /
T04TD3973E:255a-4: phyin chad shin tu legs par sngom mam /
T04TD3973E:255a-5: chos ji lta ba dang 'dul ba ji lta ba dang ston pa'i bstan pa ji lta ba bzhin du legs par sngom lags kyis /
T04TD3973E:255a-6: yang 'di ltar shes bzhin du phyin chad mi bgyid lags so zhes dang /
T04TD3973E:255a-9: ltung ba bshags pa'i cho ga thams cad yod par smra ba'i pandi ta de ba sh'a nitas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T04TD3973E:255a-11: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po d'i pam ka ra shr'i dzny'a na dang /
T04TD3973E:255a-12: bod kyi lo ts'a ba dge slong tshul khrims rgyal bas bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa//
